<div class="panelHeadBlack"> Coronavirus (COVID-19) Response: UPDATED 3/23/2020</div>
  <p>In accordance with the executive order issued by Governor Cooper on March 23, RCHS will continue to be closed to students through at least Friday, May 15. The earliest date we will be able to return is May 18. Students will continue to learn remotely through the implementation of Digital Learning Days (DLDs).  </p>
  <p>We have modified our school <a href="../events/2019-2020_Calendar_REVISED032320.pdf" target="new">calendar</a> for the next several weeks to address these issues and to maximize instructional time.</p>
  <ul>
<li>Monday, March 23 - Friday, March 27: Digital Learning Days (DLDs)      </li>
    <li>Monday, March 30 - Friday, April 3: Spring Break</li>
    <li>Monday, April 6 - Friday, May 15: Digital Learning Days (DLDs)</li>
     </ul>
   Please remember that all extracurriculars, including athletics, are postponed until further notice.
      
      <br>
